    <title>Active Backup for Business 套件激活方法</title>
    <url>/posts/14792.html</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Active-Backup-for-Business-套件激活方法"><a href="#Active-Backup-for-Business-套件激活方法" class="headerlink" title="Active Backup for Business 套件激活方法"></a>Active Backup for Business 套件激活方法</h1><h2 id="问题"><a href="#问题" class="headerlink" title="问题"></a>问题</h2><p>黑群晖在不登录的情况下无法激活<code>Active backup for Business</code> 等套件，需要使用<strong>火狐浏览器</strong>进行浏览器激活</p>
<h2 id="修改步骤"><a href="#修改步骤" class="headerlink" title="修改步骤"></a>修改步骤</h2><p>需要修改文中的<code>ip地址</code>为自己群辉的登录地址，<code>serial_number</code>为自己的SN号</p>
<p><img src="https://liuweiokay.oss-cn-beijing.aliyuncs.com/202310221517381.png" alt="image-20231022151743344"></p>
<p><strong>ABB for Active backup for Business：</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://10.10.10.10:5000/webapi/auth.cgi?api=SYNO.API.Auth&amp;version=3&amp;method=login&amp;account=admin&amp;passwd=password&amp;format=cookie</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line">http://10.10.10.10:5000/webapi/auth.cgi?api=SYNO.ActiveBackup.Activation&amp;method=set&amp;version=1&amp;activated=true&amp;serial_number=179GPDN224200</span><br><span class="line"></span><br><span class="line"># 查看激活状态</span><br><span class="line">http://10.10.10.10:5000/webapi/entry.cgi?api=SYNO.ActiveBackup.Activation&amp;method=get&amp;version=1</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>ABB for Microsoft 365：</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://10.10.10.10:5000/webapi/entry.cgi?api=SYNO.ActiveBackupOffice365&amp;method=set_activation&amp;version=1&amp;serial_number=179GPDN224200</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p><strong>ABB for Google Workspace：</strong></p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">http://10.10.10.10:5000/webapi/entry.cgi?api=SYNO.ActiveBackupGSuite&amp;method=set_activation&amp;version=1&amp;serial_number=179GPDN224200</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
